MD5

MD5

An ActionScript 3 implementation of the RSA Data Security, Inc.  MD5 Message Digest Algorithm, as defined in RFC 1321.  Copyright © 2007 Henri Torgemane

Derived from A JavaScript implementation of the same.  Version 2.1 Copyright © Paul Johnston 1999 - 2002.  Other contributors: Greg Holt, Andrew Kepert, Ydnar, Lostinet

Note

This algorithm should not be your first choice for new developements, but is included to allow interoperability with existing codes and protocols.

See LICENSE.txt for full license information.
